Howdy, Bridge Troll administrator!

A new event, "<%= @event.title %>", has been posted to Bridge Troll!

<% if @event.location %>
  <%= @event.title %> will be held at:
    <%= pretty_print_address(@event.location) %>
<% end %>

There will be <%= pluralize(@event.event_sessions.count, 'session') %>:
<% @event.event_sessions.each do |s| %>
  <%= pretty_print_session(s) %>
<% end %>

<% if @event.published %>
This event is already published, so you should be able to find it here: <%= events_path %>
<% else %>
Go see the list of unpublished events to see if this is worth approving by clicking this link: <%= unpublished_events_path %>
<% end %>